    lt: 'Perjunkite t\u0105 pa\u010di\u0105 spalv\u0105 du kartus.<br>Spustel\u0117kite fig\u016br\u0105, tada lent\u0105.<br>Vilkite u\u017e lentos, kad pa\u0161alintum\u0117te.',
    sl: 'Premaknite isto barvo dvakrat.<br>Kliknite figuro, nato polje.<br>Povlecite z deske za odstranitev.',
    lv: 'P\u0101rvietojiet to pa\u0161u kr\u0101su divreiz.<br>Noklik\u0161\u0137iniet uz fig\u016bras, tad uz lauka.<br>Velciet \u0101rpus galdi\u0146a, lai no\u0146emtu.',
